Photo Frame

This is a simple python project that displays my photo gallery on an old monitor using a raspberry pi Pico.

Hardware
    *KeyBoard
    *Mouse
    *Monitor
    *Pico
    *SD Card 128GB

Software
    *Raspberry Pi OS
    *Python3
    *Tornado Web Server
    *Jinja templates
    *Sqlite3
    *FireFox in --kiosk mode

Setup
    You will need to edit the env vars in photoframe.py to what you need.
    You will also need to edit link paths in run.sh to your needs. 